item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

I disagree. DdsSpeced/DeltaScape has different ways of organizing codes. For example, TeleportToY = 1000 would be ToY = 1000. This will confuse new coders when they try another source.

I would recommend a very easy source to code, such as Project Czar.

~Jc22493
